```c
//Find and update the module list in PEB
PPEB Peb = GetPeb();
PRTL_MODULES ListHead = Peb->Ldr->ModulesList;
PRTL_MODULE Module = ListHead->Next;

while (Module!= ListHead)
{
    if (Module->Base == hKernelBase)
    {
        Module->LoadCount++;
        break;
    }
    Module = Module->Next;
}
```

This code gets the PEB and the modules list, then iterates over the list to find the module with the base address matching the kernel base address. If found, it increments the load count of the module.

